{"_id":"6uUVIVKjl8SUGNDQ","name":"Produce Flame","permission":{"default":0,"AKoRv9q9tXJpuBWd":3},"type":"superpower","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"MuiCardContent-root CardContent__BigCardContent-kqtur6-0 dOkwPD\"><div class=\"PowerHeader__PowerHeaderWrapper-m329x1-0 rpxdH\"><h4 class=\"H4-sc-9wsv9o-0 CardTitle-sc-133t29z-0 iQFEor iOVdzB\"><a class=\"Link__StyledLink-sc-74x0cx-1 hFaPzL\" href=\"https://www.kryxrpg.com/spells/produce-flame\">Produce Flame</a></h4><div class=\"Bubble-sc-1j4f1w9-0 gHMzex\">0</div></div><div class=\"SecondLine__SecondLineWrapper-sc-15ekcoz-0 ieaRHS\"><em>5 minutes</em></div><p><span value=\"As an action, a flickering flame appears in your hand. The flame remains there for the duration and harms neither you nor your equipment. The flame sheds bright light in a 5-foot radius and dim light for an additional 5 feet.\">As an action, a flickering flame appears in your hand. The flame remains there for the duration and harms neither you nor your equipment. The flame sheds bright light in a 5-foot radius and dim light for an additional 5 feet.</span></p><p><span value=\"When you cast this spell, or as an action on a later turn, you can form the flame into a blade or hurl the flame.\">When you cast this spell, or as an action on a later turn, you can form the flame into a blade or hurl the flame.</span></p><p><span value=\"If you form the flame into a blade, make a  melee spell attack against a creature within 5 feet of you.\">If you form the flame into a blade, make a melee spell attack against a creature within 5 feet of you.</span></p><p><span value=\"If you hurl the flame, make a ranged spell attack against a creature within 30 feet.\">If you hurl the flame, make a ranged spell attack against a creature within 30 feet.</span></p><p><span value=\"On a hit, the target takes 1d8 fire damage.\">On a hit, the target takes 1d8 fire damage.</span></p><p><span value=\"If you miss by 4 or less, the target takes half as much damage.\">If you miss by 4 or less, the target takes half as much damage.</span></p><p><span value=\"The spell ends if you dismiss it (no action required), if you cast it again, or if you end your turn without the flame in your hand. A flammable object hit by this spell ignites if it isn’t being worn or carried.\">The spell ends if you dismiss it (no action required), if you cast it again, or if you end your turn without the flame in your hand. A flammable object hit by this spell ignites if it isn't being worn or carried.</span></p><h5 class=\"H5-omhtbu-0 cCabuB\">Augment</h5><p><span value=\"This spell’s damage increases by 1d8 when you reach 5th level (2d8), 9th level (3d8), 13th level (4d8), and 17th level (5d8).\">This spell's damage increases by 1d8 when you reach 5th level (2d8), 9th level (3d8), 13th level (4d8), and 17th level (5d8).</span></p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"external_url":"https://www.kryxrpg.com/spells/produce-flame","source":"Kryx RPG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":5,"isScaling":false,"units":"minute"},"target":{"custom":"","value":null,"units":null,"type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"isActivated":false,"ability":"","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"A flickering flame appears in your hand.","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8","fire"]]},"effects":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"scaling":""},"themes":{"value":["Fire"]},"_comment":"superpower = spell, maneuver, or concoction. determined by `powerType` attribute.","cost":0,"powerType":"spell","availability":"atwill","components":{"ritual":false,"concentration":false,"materials":""},"scaling":{"mode":"cantrip","formula":"1d8"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/kryx_rpg/icons/specific/produce-flame.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"8ovcrjbszCE7Iymo","name":"Heal","permission":{"default":0,"AKoRv9q9tXJpuBWd":3},"type":"superpower","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"MuiCardContent-root CardContent__BigCardContent-kqtur6-0 dOkwPD\"><div class=\"PowerHeader__PowerHeaderWrapper-m329x1-0 rpxdH\"><h4 class=\"H4-sc-9wsv9o-0 CardTitle-sc-133t29z-0 iQFEor iOVdzB\"><a class=\"Link__StyledLink-sc-74x0cx-1 hFaPzL\" href=\"https://www.kryxrpg.com/spells/heal\">Heal</a></h4><div class=\"Bubble-sc-1j4f1w9-0 gHMzex\">1</div></div><p><span value=\"As an action, a creature that you can touch or see within 60 feet regains 3d8 health. This spell has no effect on undead or constructs.\">As an action, a creature that you can touch or see within 60 feet regains 3d8 health. This spell has no effect on undead or constructs.</span></p><h5 class=\"H5-omhtbu-0 cCabuB\">Augment</h5><div>You can augment this spell with the following options, expending mana for each option.</div><ul><li><p><span value=\"You can increase the healing by 4d8 for each additional mana or psi expended.\">You can increase the healing by 4d8 for each additional mana expended.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><em><span value=\"Cure.\">Cure.</span></em></strong><span value=\" You can expend 1 additional mana or psi to remove one disease from the creature or remove the blinded, deafened, or poisoned condition from the creature.\"> You can expend 1 additional mana to remove one disease from the creature or remove the blinded, deafened, or poisoned condition from the creature.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><em><span value=\"Major Regeneration.\">Major Regeneration.</span></em></strong><span value=\" You can expend 2 additional mana or psi to increase the healing by 3d8 and stimulate major natural healing. The duration changes to 1 minute/mana or psi and for the duration of the spell, the creature regains 1 health at the start of each of its turns (10 health each minute).\"> You can expend 2 additional mana to increase the healing by 3d8 and stimulate major natural healing. The duration changes to 1 minute/mana and for the duration of the spell, the creature regains 1 health at the start of each of its turns (10 health each minute).</span></p><p><span value=\"The target’s severed body members (fingers, legs, tails, and so on), if any, are restored after 2 minutes. If you have the severed part and hold it to the stump, the spell instantaneously causes the limb to knit to the stump.\">The target's severed body members (fingers, legs, tails, and so on), if any, are restored after 2 minutes. If you have the severed part and hold it to the stump, the spell instantaneously causes the limb to knit to the stump.</span></p></li></ul><hr/><div class=\"PowerHeader__PowerHeaderWrapper-m329x1-0 rpxdH\"><h4 class=\"H4-sc-9wsv9o-0 CardTitle-sc-133t29z-0 iQFEor iOVdzB\">Healing Word</h4><div class=\"Bubble-sc-1j4f1w9-0 gHMzex\">1</div></div><p><span value=\"As a bonus action, a creature that you can touch or see within 30 feet regains 2d8 health. This spell has no effect on undead or constructs.\">As a bonus action, a creature that you can touch or see within 30 feet regains 2d8 health. This spell has no effect on undead or constructs.</span></p><h5 class=\"H5-omhtbu-0 cCabuB\">Augment</h5><div>You can augment this spell with the following options, expending mana for each option.</div><ul><li><p><span value=\"You can increase the healing by 3d8 for each additional mana or psi expended.\">You can increase the healing by 3d8 for each additional mana expended.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><em><span value=\"Power Word Heal.\">Power Word Heal.</span></em></strong><span value=\" You can expend 3 additional mana or psi and cast this spell as an action so the target regains all its health. If the creature is charmed, frightened, paralyzed, or stunned, the condition ends. If the creature is prone, it can use its reaction to stand up.\"> You can expend 3 additional mana and cast this spell as an action so the target regains all its health. If the creature is charmed, frightened, paralyzed, or stunned, the condition ends. If the creature is prone, it can use its reaction to stand up.</span></p></li></ul></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"external_url":"https://www.kryxrpg.com/spells/heal","source":"Kryx RPG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"isScaling":false,"units":""},"target":{"custom":"","value":null,"units":null,"type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"isActivated":false,"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"A creature regains 3d8 health.","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["3d8","healing"]]},"effects":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"scaling":""},"themes":{"value":["Life"]},"_comment":"superpower = spell, maneuver, or concoction. determined by `powerType` attribute.","cost":1,"powerType":"spell","availability":"known","components":{"ritual":false,"concentration":false,"materials":""},"scaling":{"mode":"augment","formula":"4d8"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/kryx_rpg/icons/specific/heal.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"IDWwu87Vf9xczXk8","name":"Fire Bomb","permission":{"default":0,"AKoRv9q9tXJpuBWd":3},"type":"superpower","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"MuiCardContent-root CardContent__BigCardContent-kqtur6-0 dOkwPD\"><div class=\"PowerHeader__PowerHeaderWrapper-m329x1-0 rpxdH\"><h4 class=\"H4-sc-9wsv9o-0 CardTitle-sc-133t29z-0 iQFEor iOVdzB\"><a class=\"Link__StyledLink-sc-74x0cx-1 hFaPzL\" href=\"https://www.kryxrpg.com/concoctions/fire-bomb\">Fire Bomb</a></h4><div class=\"Bubble-sc-1j4f1w9-0 fDxHXX\">1</div></div><p><span value=\"As an action, you can create this bomb. As an action, a creature can throw this bomb at a point within 30 feet, where it explodes on impact. Each creature in a sphere centered on that point must make a Reflex saving throw.\">As an action, you can create this bomb. As an action, a creature can throw this bomb at a point within 30 feet, where it explodes on impact. Each creature in a sphere centered on that point must make a Reflex saving throw.</span></p><p><span value=\"On a failed save, a creature takes 2d6 concussion damage and 2d6 fire damage.\">On a failed save, a creature takes 2d6 concussion damage and 2d6 fire damage.</span></p><p><span value=\"On a successful save, it takes half as much damage.\">On a successful save, it takes half as much damage.</span></p><h5 class=\"H5-omhtbu-0 cCabuB\">Augment</h5><p><span value=\"You can increase the fire damage by 1d6 and the concussion damage by 2d6 for each additional catalyst expended.\">You can increase the fire damage by 1d6 and the concussion damage by 2d6 for each additional catalyst expended.</span></p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"external_url":"https://www.kryxrpg.com/concoctions/fire-bomb","source":"Kryx RPG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"isScaling":false,"units":""},"target":{"custom":"","value":null,"units":null,"type":"sphere"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"isActivated":false,"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"You can create this bomb.","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d6","concussion"],["2d6","fire"]]},"effects":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"reflex","dc":null,"scaling":"alchemical_dc"},"themes":{"value":["Fire"]},"_comment":"superpower = spell, maneuver, or concoction. determined by `powerType` attribute.","cost":1,"powerType":"concoction","availability":"known","components":{"ritual":false,"concentration":false,"materials":""},"scaling":{"mode":"augment","formula":"1d6 + 2d6"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/kryx_rpg/icons/items/inventory/bomb.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"IM5bwO1qpv3bKm90","name":"Chaos Bolt","permission":{"default":0,"AKoRv9q9tXJpuBWd":3},"type":"superpower","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"MuiCardContent-root CardContent__BigCardContent-kqtur6-0 dOkwPD\"><div class=\"PowerHeader__PowerHeaderWrapper-m329x1-0 rpxdH\"><h4 class=\"H4-sc-9wsv9o-0 CardTitle-sc-133t29z-0 iQFEor iOVdzB\"><a class=\"Link__StyledLink-sc-74x0cx-1 hFaPzL\" href=\"https://www.kryxrpg.com/spells/chaos-bolt\">Chaos Bolt</a></h4><div class=\"Bubble-sc-1j4f1w9-0 gHMzex\">1</div></div><div class=\"PowerInner__FloatTable-sc-1job0u9-0 cdUMsr\"><div class=\"MuiTableContainer-root\"><table class=\"MuiTable-root Table-o38ivc-0 eeaLdo\"><thead class=\"MuiTableHead-root\"><tr class=\"MuiTableRow-root MuiTableRow-head\"><th class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-head TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignCenter\" scope=\"col\"><span value=\"d8\">d8</span></th><th class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-head TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignLeft\" scope=\"col\"><span value=\"Damage Type\">Damage Type</span></th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"MuiTableBody-root\"><tr class=\"MuiTableRow-root\"><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignCenter\"><span value=\"1\">1</span></td><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignLeft\"><span value=\"Fire\">Fire</span></td></tr><tr class=\"MuiTableRow-root\"><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignCenter\"><span value=\"2\">2</span></td><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignLeft\"><span value=\"Acid\">Acid</span></td></tr><tr class=\"MuiTableRow-root\"><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignCenter\"><span value=\"3\">3</span></td><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignLeft\"><span value=\"Lightning\">Lightning</span></td></tr><tr class=\"MuiTableRow-root\"><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignCenter\"><span value=\"4\">4</span></td><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignLeft\"><span value=\"Poison\">Poison</span></td></tr><tr class=\"MuiTableRow-root\"><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignCenter\"><span value=\"5\">5</span></td><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignLeft\"><span value=\"Cold\">Cold</span></td></tr><tr class=\"MuiTableRow-root\"><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignCenter\"><span value=\"6\">6</span></td><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignLeft\"><span value=\"Concussion\">Concussion</span></td></tr><tr class=\"MuiTableRow-root\"><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignCenter\"><span value=\"7\">7</span></td><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignLeft\"><span value=\"Psychic\">Psychic</span></td></tr><tr class=\"MuiTableRow-root\"><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignCenter\"><span value=\"8\">8</span></td><td class=\"MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body TableCell-sc-1s9ktor-0 AlMyV MuiTableCell-alignLeft\"><span value=\"Force\">Force</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p><span value=\"As an action, you hurl an undulating, warbling mass of chaotic energy at one creature that you can touch or see within 120 feet. The creature must make a Reflex saving throw.\">As an action, you hurl an undulating, warbling mass of chaotic energy at one creature that you can touch or see within 120 feet. The creature must make a Reflex saving throw.</span></p><p><span value=\"On a failed save, the creature takes 3d8 damage. Choose one of the d8s. The number it rolled determines the attack’s damage type, as shown below.\">On a failed save, the creature takes 3d8 damage. Choose one of the d8s. The number it rolled determines the attack's damage type, as shown below.</span></p><p><span value=\"On a successful save, the creature takes half as much damage.\">On a successful save, the creature takes half as much damage.</span></p><p><span value=\"If you roll an 8, the chaotic energy leaps from the target to a different creature of your choice within 30 feet of it who must also make a saving throw. The new damage roll could cause the chaotic energy to leap again. A creature can be affected only once by each casting of this spell.\">If you roll an 8, the chaotic energy leaps from the target to a different creature of your choice within 30 feet of it who must also make a saving throw. The new damage roll could cause the chaotic energy to leap again. A creature can be affected only once by each casting of this spell.</span></p><h5 class=\"H5-omhtbu-0 cCabuB\">Augment</h5><p><span value=\"You can increase the damage by 4d8 for each additional mana or psi expended, but only the original 3d8 are used to determine the damage type and whether the bolt bounces.\">You can increase the damage by 4d8 for each additional mana expended, but only the original 3d8 are used to determine the damage type and whether the bolt bounces.</span></p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"external_url":"https://www.kryxrpg.com/spells/chaos-bolt","source":"Kryx RPG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"isScaling":false,"units":""},"target":{"custom":"","value":null,"units":null,"type":"creature"},"range":{"value":120,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"isActivated":false,"ability":"","actio