{"_id":"WTrdUFFFUPJCzFj5","name":"Illusory Ink","permission":{"default":0,"AKoRv9q9tXJpuBWd":3},"type":"superpower","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"MuiCardContent-root CardContent__BigCardContent-kqtur6-0 dOkwPD\"><div class=\"PowerHeader__PowerHeaderWrapper-m329x1-0 rpxdH\"><h4 class=\"H4-sc-9wsv9o-0 CardTitle-sc-133t29z-0 iQFEor iOVdzB\"><a class=\"Link__StyledLink-sc-74x0cx-1 hFaPzL\" href=\"https://www.kryxrpg.com/concoctions/illusory-ink\">Illusory Ink</a></h4><div class=\"Bubble-sc-1j4f1w9-0 fDxHXX\">1</div></div><div class=\"SecondLine__SecondLineWrapper-sc-15ekcoz-0 ieaRHS\"><em>10 days</em></div><p><span value=\"As you spend 1 minute to write on parchment, paper, or some other suitable writing material, the ink you use transforms into a potent illusion that lasts for the duration.\">As you spend 1 minute to write on parchment, paper, or some other suitable writing material, the ink you use transforms into a potent illusion that lasts for the duration.</span></p><p><span value=\"To you and any creatures you designate when you create the writing, the writing appears normal, written in your hand, and conveys whatever meaning you intended when you wrote the text. To all others, the writing appears as if it were written in an unknown or magical script that is unintelligible. Alternatively, you can cause the writing to appear to be an entirely different message, written in a different hand and language, though the language must be one you know.\">To you and any creatures you designate when you create the writing, the writing appears normal, written in your hand, and conveys whatever meaning you intended when you wrote the text. To all others, the writing appears as if it were written in an unknown or magical script that is unintelligible. Alternatively, you can cause the writing to appear to be an entirely different message, written in a different hand and language, though the language must be one you know.</span></p><p><span value=\"Should the effect be dispelled, the original script and the illusion both disappear.\">Should the effect be dispelled, the original script and the illusion both disappear.</span></p><p><span value=\"A creature with truesight can read the hidden message.\">A creature with truesight can read the hidden message.</span></p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"external_url":"https://www.kryxrpg.com/concoctions/illusory-ink","source":"Kryx RPG","activation":{"type":"1 minute","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"isScaling":false,"units":"day"},"target":{"custom":"","value":null,"units":null,"type":"object"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"isActivated":false,"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"Paper, or some other suitable writing material, the ink you use transforms into a potent illusion.","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[]},"effects":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"scaling":""},"themes":{"value":["Deceit"]},"_comment":"superpower = spell, maneuver, or concoction. determined by `powerType` attribute.","cost":1,"powerType":"concoction","availability":"known","components":{"ritual":false,"concentration":false,"materials":""},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/kryx_rpg/icons/items/inventory/feather-green-stripe.jpg"}
{"_id":"lIDJASWj2je3k8wU","name":"Acid Breath","permission":{"default":0,"AKoRv9q9tXJpuBWd":3},"type":"superpower","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"MuiCardContent-root CardContent__BigCardContent-kqtur6-0 dOkwPD\"><div class=\"PowerHeader__PowerHeaderWrapper-m329x1-0 rpxdH\"><h4 class=\"H4-sc-9wsv9o-0 CardTitle-sc-133t29z-0 iQFEor iOVdzB\"><a class=\"Link__StyledLink-sc-74x0cx-1 hFaPzL\" href=\"https://www.kryxrpg.com/concoctions/acid-breath\">Acid Breath</a></h4><div class=\"Bubble-sc-1j4f1w9-0 fDxHXX\">1</div></div><p><span value=\"As an action, you can create a vial of liquid that smells of sulfur. A creature can take the contents into their mouth and spit it out as an action as a green corrosive mist shoots forth. Each creature in a cone or line must make a Reflex saving throw.\">As an action, you can create a vial of liquid that smells of sulfur. A creature can take the contents into their mouth and spit it out as an action as a green corrosive mist shoots forth. Each creature in a cone or line must make a Reflex saving throw.</span></p><p><span value=\"On a failed save, a creature takes 3d8 acid damage immediately and additional acid damage equal to half the amount of acid damage dealt at the end of its next turn.\">On a failed save, a creature takes 3d8 acid damage immediately and additional acid damage equal to half the amount of acid damage dealt at the end of its next turn.</span></p><p><span value=\"On a successful save, a creature takes half the initial damage and no damage at the end of its next turn.\">On a successful save, a creature takes half the initial damage and no damage at the end of its next turn.</span></p><p><span value=\"A creature killed by this spell is affected by rigor mortis.\">A creature killed by this spell is affected by rigor mortis.</span></p><h5 class=\"H5-omhtbu-0 cCabuB\">Augment</h5><p><span value=\"You can increase the damage by 2d8 for each additional catalyst expended.\">You can increase the damage by 2d8 for each additional catalyst expended.</span></p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"external_url":"https://www.kryxrpg.com/concoctions/acid-breath","source":"Kryx RPG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"isScaling":false,"units":""},"target":{"custom":"","value":null,"units":null,"type":"coneOrLine"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"isActivated":false,"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"You can create a vial of liquid that smells of sulfur.","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["3d8","acid"]]},"effects":{"parts":[["plus half that much damage again later"]]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"reflex","dc":null,"scaling":"alchemical_dc"},"themes":{"value":["Acid"]},"_comment":"superpower = spell, maneuver, or concoction. determined by `powerType` attribute.","cost":1,"powerType":"concoction","availability":"known","components":{"ritual":false,"concentration":false,"materials":""},"scaling":{"mode":"augment","formula":"2d8"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/kryx_rpg/icons/items/potions/major-green.jpg"}
{"_id":"n2OX6BKiX8UjUcmR","name":"Burning Hands","permission":{"default":0,"AKoRv9q9tXJpuBWd":3},"type":"superpower","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"MuiCardContent-root CardContent__BigCardContent-kqtur6-0 dOkwPD\"><div class=\"PowerHeader__PowerHeaderWrapper-m329x1-0 rpxdH\"><h4 class=\"H4-sc-9wsv9o-0 CardTitle-sc-133t29z-0 iQFEor iOVdzB\"><a class=\"Link__StyledLink-sc-74x0cx-1 hFaPzL\" href=\"https://www.kryxrpg.com/spells/burning-hands\">Burning Hands</a></h4><div class=\"Bubble-sc-1j4f1w9-0 gHMzex\">1</div></div><p><span value=\"As an action, you hold your hands with thumbs touching and fingers spread as a thin sheet of flames shoots forth from your outstretched fingertips. Each creature in a cone or line must make a Reflex saving throw.\">As an action, you hold your hands with thumbs touching and fingers spread as a thin sheet of flames shoots forth from your outstretched fingertips. Each creature in a cone or line must make a Reflex saving throw.</span></p><p><span value=\"On a failed save, a creature takes 3d6 fire damage and is burning 1.\">On a failed save, a creature takes 3d6 fire damage and is burning 1.</span></p><p><span value=\"On a successful save, a creature takes half as much damage and doesn’t start burning.\">On a successful save, a creature takes half as much damage and doesn't start burning.</span></p><p><span value=\"The fire ignites any flammable objects in the area that aren’t being worn or carried.\">The fire ignites any flammable objects in the area that aren't being worn or carried.</span></p><h5 class=\"H5-omhtbu-0 cCabuB\">Augment</h5><p><span value=\"You can increase the damage by 2d6 and the burning level by 1 for each additional mana or psi expended.\">You can increase the damage by 2d6 and the burning level by 1 for each additional mana expended.</span></p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"external_url":"https://www.kryxrpg.com/spells/burning-hands","source":"Kryx RPG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"isScaling":false,"units":""},"target":{"custom":"","value":null,"units":null,"type":"coneOrLine"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"isActivated":false,"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"You hold your hands with thumbs touching and fingers spread as a thin sheet of flames shoots forth from your outstretched fingertips.","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["3d6","fire"]]},"effects":{"parts":[["burning 1"]]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"reflex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell_dc"},"themes":{"value":["Fire"]},"_comment":"superpower = spell, maneuver, or concoction. determined by `powerType` attribute.","cost":1,"powerType":"spell","availability":"known","components":{"ritual":false,"concentration":false,"materials":""},"scaling":{"mode":"augment","formula":"2d6"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/kryx_rpg/icons/spells/beam-red-2.jpg"}
{"_id":"nZa93jX2CAoNqBdb","name":"Sneak","permission":{"default":0,"AKoRv9q9tXJpuBWd":3},"type":"superpower","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"MuiCardContent-root CardContent__BigCardContent-kqtur6-0 wdlNQ\"><div class=\"PowerHeader__PowerHeaderWrapper-m329x1-0 hTRuQY\"><h4 class=\"H4-sc-9wsv9o-0 CardTitle-sc-133t29z-0 eTNkmV\"><a class=\"Link__StyledLink-sc-74x0cx-1 irukdI\" href=\"https://www.kryxrpg.com/maneuvers/sneak\">Sneak</a></h4><div class=\"Bubble-sc-1j4f1w9-0 fHOPmY\">1</div></div><p>As a reaction, which you take when you make a Stealth check, you move with precision and stealth. You have a +2 bonus on the triggering Stealth ability check.</p><p>You can use this maneuver before or after the ability check is made, but before any effects of the check are applied.</p><h5 class=\"H5-omhtbu-0 eMNyC\">Enhance</h5><p>You can expend 1 additional stamina die to instead have advantage on the Stealth ability check</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"external_url":"https://www.kryxrpg.com/maneuvers/sneak","source":"Kryx RPG","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":null,"condition":"when you make a stealth check"},"duration":{"value":null,"isScaling":false,"units":""},"target":{"custom":"","value":null,"units":null,"type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"isActivated":false,"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"You move with precision and stealth.","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[]},"effects":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"scaling":""},"themes":{"value":["Beast","Shadow"]},"_comment":"superpower = spell, maneuver, or concoction. determined by `powerType` attribute.","cost":1,"powerType":"maneuver","availability":"known","components":{"ritual":false,"concentration":false,"materials":""},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/kryx_rpg/icons/specific/pass-without-trace.jpg