{"_id":"nf4hkXq73ZaFeqxM","name":"Healing Word","permission":{"default":0,"AKoRv9q9tXJpuBWd":3},"type":"superpower","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"MuiCardContent-root CardContent__BigCardContent-kqtur6-0 dOkwPD\"><div class=\"PowerHeader__PowerHeaderWrapper-m329x1-0 rpxdH\"><h4 class=\"H4-sc-9wsv9o-0 CardTitle-sc-133t29z-0 iQFEor iOVdzB\"><a class=\"Link__StyledLink-sc-74x0cx-1 hFaPzL\" href=\"https://www.kryxrpg.com/spells/heal\">Heal</a></h4><div class=\"Bubble-sc-1j4f1w9-0 gHMzex\">1</div></div><p><span value=\"As an action, a creature that you can touch or see within 60 feet regains 3d8 health. This spell has no effect on undead or constructs.\">As an action, a creature that you can touch or see within 60 feet regains 3d8 health. This spell has no effect on undead or constructs.</span></p><h5 class=\"H5-omhtbu-0 cCabuB\">Augment</h5><div>You can augment this spell with the following options, expending mana for each option.</div><ul><li><p><span value=\"You can increase the healing by 4d8 for each additional mana or psi expended.\">You can increase the healing by 4d8 for each additional mana expended.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><em><span value=\"Cure.\">Cure.</span></em></strong><span value=\" You can expend 1 additional mana or psi to remove one disease from the creature or remove the blinded, deafened, or poisoned condition from the creature.\"> You can expend 1 additional mana to remove one disease from the creature or remove the blinded, deafened, or poisoned condition from the creature.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><em><span value=\"Major Regeneration.\">Major Regeneration.</span></em></strong><span value=\" You can expend 2 additional mana or psi to increase the healing by 3d8 and stimulate major natural healing. The duration changes to 1 minute/mana or psi and for the duration of the spell, the creature regains 1 health at the start of each of its turns (10 health each minute).\"> You can expend 2 additional mana to increase the healing by 3d8 and stimulate major natural healing. The duration changes to 1 minute/mana and for the duration of the spell, the creature regains 1 health at the start of each of its turns (10 health each minute).</span></p><p><span value=\"The target’s severed body members (fingers, legs, tails, and so on), if any, are restored after 2 minutes. If you have the severed part and hold it to the stump, the spell instantaneously causes the limb to knit to the stump.\">The target's severed body members (fingers, legs, tails, and so on), if any, are restored after 2 minutes. If you have the severed part and hold it to the stump, the spell instantaneously causes the limb to knit to the stump.</span></p></li></ul><hr/><div class=\"PowerHeader__PowerHeaderWrapper-m329x1-0 rpxdH\"><h4 class=\"H4-sc-9wsv9o-0 CardTitle-sc-133t29z-0 iQFEor iOVdzB\">Healing Word</h4><div class=\"Bubble-sc-1j4f1w9-0 gHMzex\">1</div></div><p><span value=\"As a bonus action, a creature that you can touch or see within 30 feet regains 2d8 health. This spell has no effect on undead or constructs.\">As a bonus action, a creature that you can touch or see within 30 feet regains 2d8 health. This spell has no effect on undead or constructs.</span></p><h5 class=\"H5-omhtbu-0 cCabuB\">Augment</h5><div>You can augment this spell with the following options, expending mana for each option.</div><ul><li><p><span value=\"You can increase the healing by 3d8 for each additional mana or psi expended.\">You can increase the healing by 3d8 for each additional mana expended.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><em><span value=\"Power Word Heal.\">Power Word Heal.</span></em></strong><span value=\" You can expend 3 additional mana or psi and cast this spell as an action so the target regains all its health. If the creature is charmed, frightened, paralyzed, or stunned, the condition ends. If the creature is prone, it can use its reaction to stand up.\"> You can expend 3 additional mana and cast this spell as an action so the target regains all its health. If the creature is charmed, frightened, paralyzed, or stunned, the condition ends. If the creature is prone, it can use its reaction to stand up.</span></p></li></ul></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"external_url":"https://www.kryxrpg.com/spells/heal","source":"Kryx RPG","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"isScaling":false,"units":""},"target":{"custom":"","value":null,"units":null,"type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"isActivated":false,"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"A creature regains 2d8 health.","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","healing"]]},"effects":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"scaling":""},"themes":{"value":["Life"]},"_comment":"superpower = spell, maneuver, or concoction. determined by `powerType` attribute.","cost":1,"powerType":"spell","availability":"known","components":{"ritual":false,"concentration":false,"materials":""},"scaling":{"mode":"augment","formula":"3d8"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/kryx_rpg/icons/specific/heal.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"q5Z04qQoLMoCVHBy","name":"Disorient","permission":{"default":0,"AKoRv9q9tXJpuBWd":3},"type":"superpower","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"MuiCardContent-root CardContent__BigCardContent-kqtur6-0 dOkwPD\"><div class=\"PowerHeader__PowerHeaderWrapper-m329x1-0 rpxdH\"><h4 class=\"H4-sc-9wsv9o-0 CardTitle-sc-133t29z-0 iQFEor iOVdzB\"><a class=\"Link__StyledLink-sc-74x0cx-1 hFaPzL\" href=\"https://www.kryxrpg.com/maneuvers/disorient\">Disorient</a></h4><div class=\"Bubble-sc-1j4f1w9-0 dGTqJj\">1</div></div><p><span value=\"As a bonus action when you hit a creature with a melee weapon attack, you can disorient the target. The target must make a Fortitude saving throw.\">As a bonus action when you hit a creature with a melee weapon attack, you can disorient the target. The target must make a Fortitude saving throw.</span></p><p><span value=\"On a failed save, add the stamina die to the attack’s damage roll and the target can’t take reactions until the start of its next turn.\">On a failed save, add the stamina die to the attack's damage roll and the target can't take reactions until the start of its next turn.</span></p><p><span value=\"On a successful save the target takes half as much damage.\">On a successful save the target takes half as much damage.</span></p><h5 class=\"H5-omhtbu-0 cCabuB\">Enhance</h5><div>You can augment this maneuver with the following options, expending stamina dice for each option.</div><ul><li><p><span value=\"You can increase the damage for each additional stamina die expended.\">You can increase the damage for each additional stamina die expended.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><em><span value=\"Stagger.\">Stagger.</span></em></strong><span value=\" You can expend 1 additional stamina die so the target is staggered until the end of its next turn.\"> You can expend 1 additional stamina die so the target is staggered until the end of its next turn.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><em><span value=\"Stun.\">Stun.</span></em></strong><span value=\" You can expend 3 additional stamina die so the target is stunned until the end of its next turn.\"> You can expend 3 additional stamina die so the target is stunned until the end of its next turn.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><em><span value=\"Paralyze.\">Paralyze.</span></em></strong><span value=\" You can expend 4 additional stamina dice so the target is paralyzed until the end of its next turn.\"> You can expend 4 additional stamina dice so the target is paralyzed until the end of its next turn.</span></p></li></ul></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"external_url":"https://www.kryxrpg.com/maneuvers/disorient","source":"Kryx RPG","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":null,"condition":"when you hit a creature with a melee weapon attack"},"duration":{"value":null,"isScaling":false,"units":""},"target":{"custom":"","value":null,"units":null,"type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"isActivated":false,"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"You can disorient a creature.","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8","same"]]},"effects":{"parts":[["can't take reactions"]]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"fortitude","dc":null,"scaling":"maneuver_dc"},"themes":{"value":["Earth","Vanguard"]},"_comment":"superpower = spell, maneuver, or concoction. determined by `powerType` attribute.","cost":1,"powerType":"maneuver","availability":"known","components":{"ritual":false,"concentration":false,"materials":""},"scaling":{"mode":"enhance","formula":"1d8"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/kryx_rpg/icons/skills/ice_15.jpg"}
